classDiagram
    class Car {
        - String make
        - String model
        - int year
        - String licensePlate
        - boolean available
        + Car(String make, String model, int year, String licensePlate)
        + boolean isAvailable()
        + void rent()
        + void returnCar()
    }
    class Customer {
        - String name
        - String email
        - String phoneNumber
        + Customer(String name, String email, String phoneNumber)
        + String getName()
        + String getEmail()
        + String getPhoneNumber()
        + void rentCar(Car car)
        + void returnCar(Car car)
    }
    class RentalSystem {
        - List<Car> cars
        - List<Customer> customers
        + RentalSystem()
        + void addCar(Car car)
        + void addCustomer(Customer customer)
        + List<Car> getAvailableCars()
        + void rentCar(Customer customer, Car car)
        + void returnCar(Customer customer, Car car)
    }

@startuml
!define USER actor
!define SYSTEM usecase

USER User as "End User"
USER Admin as "Administrator"

SYSTEM ChatGPT as "ChatGPT Clone"
SYSTEM ImageGen as "Image Generator"
SYSTEM Chatbot as "Chatbot"
SYSTEM UserInterface as "User Interface"
SYSTEM OpenAIAPI as "OpenAI API"
SYSTEM Database as "Database"

User --> (Initiate Chat)
User --> (Request Image)
User --> (Engage Chatbot)
User --> (Utilize AI Functionalities)
User --> (Store Data)

Admin --> (Manage Users)
Admin --> (Monitor Conversations)
Admin --> (Analyze Usage Data)

(Initiate Chat) --> ChatGPT
(Request Image) --> ImageGen
(Engage Chatbot) --> Chatbot
(Utilize AI Functionalities) --> OpenAIAPI
(Store Data) --> Database

ChatGPT --> (Provide Response)
ImageGen --> (Generate Image)
Chatbot --> (Interact with User)
OpenAIAPI --> (Process Requests)
Database --> (Store and Retrieve Data)

@enduml
